<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.6">
<l>maṇmakaḷ kēḷvaṉ malarmaṅkai nāyakaṉ nantaṉ peṟṟa matalai</l>
<l>yaṇṇa lilaikkuḻa lūtinam cērikkē yalliṟṟāṉ vanta piṉṉai</l>
<l>kaṇmalar cōrntu mulaivantu vimmik kamalaccev vāyve ḷuppa</l>
<l>veṉmakaḷ vaṇṇa mirukkiṉṟa vānaṅkā yeṉceykē ṉeṉcey kēṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>After the beloved of the earth maid, hero of the lotus lady,</l>
<l rend="indent">the child that Nanda has,</l>
<l>The ruler came to our neighborhood blowing his petal[-adorned] flute</l>
<l rend="indent">in the night,</l>
<l>Oh, the way my daughter’s complexion is,</l>
<l rend="indent">her breasts continually heaving,</l>
<l>Her bud[-like] eyes weeping, as her lotus-red lips grow pale!</l>
<l rend="indent">Lady,  What do I do? What do I do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
